<p><!-- x-tinymce/html --></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体;">录取新生应征入伍保留入学资格办理流程</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 63px; background: rgb(54, 95, 147); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 18px;">1</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(54, 95, 147); letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">递交材料（</span>IBM<span style="font-family: 宋体;">楼三楼教务处）</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">入伍通知书、录取通知书及身份证（三个材料的原件及复印件）；</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">两份《应征入伍普通高校录取新生保留入学资格申请表》（照片已贴、当地武装部已盖章）</span></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 63px; background: rgb(54, 95, 147); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 18px;">2</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(54, 95, 147); letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">登记信息（</span>IBM<span style="font-family: 宋体;">楼三楼教务处）</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">登记个人信息</span></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 63px; background: rgb(54, 95, 147); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 18px;">3</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(54, 95, 147); letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">领取资料（</span>IBM<span style="font-family: 宋体;">楼三楼教务处）</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">《保留入学资格通知书》</span></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 63px; background: rgb(54, 95, 147); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #ffffff; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 18px;">4</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(54, 95, 147); letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">盖章材料（行政楼三楼</span>307<span style="font-family: 宋体;">室）</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">两份《应征入伍普通高校录取新生保留入学资格申请表》递交学校校办盖章，一份留校备案，一份递交当地武装部。</span></span></p><p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;">注意事项</span></strong></p><p style="text-align: justify; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">1.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">请入伍新生妥善保管《保留入学资格通知书》，退伍后两年内凭《保留入学资格通知书》、退伍证及身份证办理复学；</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">2.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">若出现不当兵返回学校就读的情况，请及时联系学校教务处注册学籍，否则就读无效。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">3.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">学校地址：江西省南昌市湾里区罗亭镇江西软件职业技术大学教务处</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-family: Calibri;">4.<span style="font-family: 宋体;">联系电话：（</span>0791<span style="font-family: 宋体;">）</span>83792933</span></p><p><br/></p>